msgstr "Checagens em Tempo de Execução:"

#: ../../c-api/memory.rst:599
msgid ""
"Detect API violations. For example, detect if :c:func:`PyObject_Free` is "
"called on a memory block allocated by :c:func:`PyMem_Malloc`."
